<% const _src = srcPath; const _public = publicPath; %>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <%- include(`${_src}/views/layout/head.ejs`, {meta_title: ''}) %>
  <style>
    .kendo-ui-examples {
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .kendo-ui-examples h2,
    .kendo-ui-examples h3 {
      margin-top: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    /* 2. Custom CSS로 크기 조절 */
    .my-custom-size-button {
      padding: 12px 24px; /* 원하는 패딩 값 */
      font-size: 1.2em; /* 원하는 폰트 크기 */
    }
    .k-radio-label {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      /* Adjust alignment as needed */
    }
    .k-radio-label-text {
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .k-radio-label-description {
      font-size: 0.8em;
      color: #666;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }
  </style>
  <body>
    <%- include(`${_src}/views/layout/header.ejs`) %>
    <h1 class="!text-[30px]">guide 222<%= APP_ENV_URL %></h1>

    <!-- public 이미지 링크 테스트  -->
    <!-- <img src="<%= _public %>/resources/images/camera.png" alt="test" style="width: 300px" />-->

    <div class="vits-wrapper">11111</div>

    <section class="kendo-ui-examples">
      <h2>Kendo UI Examples</h2>

      <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl!">Buttons</h3>
      <p>버튼 크기를 키우는 방법은 두 가지가 있습니다.</p>

      <h4>1. Kendo UI 내장 클래스 사용</h4>
      <p><code>k-button-lg</code> 클래스를 추가하여 Kendo 테마에서 제공하는 큰 사이즈를 사용할 수 있습니다.</p>
      <div>
        <button id="kendoButton" type="button">Default Button</button>
        <button id="kendoPrimaryButton" type="button" class="k-primary">Primary Button</button>
        <button id="kendoLargeButton" type="button" class="k-button-lg k-primary">Large Button (k-button-lg)</button>
      </div>

      <h4 style="margin-top: 20px">2. Custom CSS 사용</h4>
      <p>
        원하는 크기로 직접 스타일을 지정할 수 있습니다. 아래 버튼은 <code>my-custom-size-button</code> 클래스를
        가집니다.
      </p>
      <div>
        <button id="customSizedButton" class="my-custom-size-button">Custom Size Button</button>
      </div>

      <h4 style="margin-top: 20px">3. Templated Button</h4>
      <div id="templatedButtonContainer"></div>

      <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl!">Radio Buttons</h3>
      <ul class="fieldlist">
        <li>
          <input type="radio" name="engine" id="engine1" />
        </li>
        <li>
          <input type="radio" name="engine" id="engine2" />
        </li>
        <li>
          <input type="radio" name="engine" id="engine3" />
        </li>
      </ul>
      <ul id="radiogroup"></ul>
      <ul id="radiogroup2"></ul>

      <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl!">Bar Chart</h3>
      <!-- <div id="chart"></div> -->

      <style>
        .cards-container {
          display: flex;
          flex-wrap: wrap;
          justify-content: center;
        }

        .k-card {
          width: 285px;
          margin: 5%;
        }

        .k-card-footer {
          text-align: center;
        }

        .k-card-action > .k-button {
          width: 100%;
        }
      </style>
      <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl!">Cards</h3>
      <div class="cards-container">
        <div class="k-card">
          <div class="k-card-header">
            <h5 class="k-card-title">Rome</h5>
            <h6 class="k-card-subtitle">Capital of Italy</h6>
          </div>
          <!-- <img alt="Kendo UI for jQuery Card Colosseum in Rome" class="k-card-media" src="" /> -->
          <div class="k-card-body">
            <p>
              Rome is a sprawling, cosmopolitan city with nearly 3,000 years of globally influential art, architecture
              and culture on display.
            </p>
            <p>Ancient ruins such as the Forum and the Colosseum evoke the power of the former Roman Empire.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="k-card-footer">
            <a class="k-button k-button-flat-base k-button-flat k-button-md k-rounded-md k-icon-button"
              ><span class="k-button-icon facebook"></span
            ></a>
            <a class="k-button k-button-flat-base k-button-flat k-button-md k-rounded-md k-icon-button"
              ><span class="k-button-icon pinterest"></span
            ></a>
            <a class="k-button k-button-flat-base k-button-flat k-button-md k-rounded-md k-icon-button"
              ><span class="k-button-icon twitter"></span
            ></a>
          </div>
          <div class="k-actions k-card-actions k-actions-stretched">
            <span class="k-card-action"
              ><button class="k-button k-button-flat-primary k-button-flat k-button-md k-rounded-md">Map</button></span
            >
            <span class="k-card-action"
              ><button class="k-button k-button-flat-primary k-button-flat k-button-md k-rounded-md">
                Weather
              </button></span
            >
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="k-card">
          <div class="k-card-header">
            <h5 class="k-card-title">Barcelona</h5>
          </div>
          <!-- <img alt="Kendo UI for jQuery Card Arc de Triomf" class="k-card-media" src="../content/web/cards/barcelona.jpg" /> -->
          <div class="k-card-body">
            <p>
              Barcelona, the cosmopolitan capital of Spain's Catalonia region, is known for its art and architecture.
            </p>
            <p>
              The fantastical Sagrada Família church and other modernist landmarks designed by Antoni Gaudí dot the
              city.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="k-actions k-card-actions">
            <button class="k-button k-button-flat-primary k-button-flat k-button-md k-rounded-md">Map</button>
            <button class="k-button k-button-flat-primary k-button-flat k-button-md k-rounded-md">Weather</button>
          </div>
          <div class="k-card-footer">
            <a class="k-button k-button-flat-base k-button-flat k-button-md k-rounded-md k-icon-button"
              ><span class="k-button-icon facebook"></span
            ></a>
            <a class="k-button k-button-flat-base k-button-flat k-button-md k-rounded-md k-icon-button"
              ><span class="k-button-icon pinterest"></span
            ></a>
            <a class="k-button k-button-flat-base k-button-flat k-button-md k-rounded-md k-icon-button"
              ><span class="k-button-icon twitter"></span
            ></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <%- include(`${_src}/views/layout/footer.ejs`) %> <%- include(`${_src}/views/layout/footer.links.ejs`) %>

    <script></script>
    <script>
      kendo.ui.icon($('.facebook'), {icon: 'facebook'});
      kendo.ui.icon($('.pinterest'), {icon: 'pinterest'});
      kendo.ui.icon($('.twitter'), {icon: 'twitter'});
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
